xploration\",  plotOutput(\"mainPlot\"), plotOutput(\"net\")),\n        tabPanel(\"Error\", textOutput(\"MSE\"),plotOutput(\"boxPlot\")),\n        tabPanel(\"Data\",  tableOutput(\"df\"))\n      )\n  \n    )\n  )\n))\n",
